  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the changes in macular function during anti-VEGF
      treatment for neovascular age-related macular degeneration.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Macular function will be investigated using visual acuity, contrast sensitivity, mfERG and
      microperimetry.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
